    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cardiovascular-simulation-lab-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2, Class II CPB device. Six factors appropriately scoped out under MRL 2 framework. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD hemolysis predictions within 20% of experimental data across the CPB operating envelope described in the bound requirement (3–6 L/min, 1750–3500 RPM). The model is accepted for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application context documented in the claim and requirement nodes.",
